txt.en: 'Hey, goin' to Rohan are ya? I have some pretty sweet gear for you. Let's see... what class are you? [placeholder] huh? \n\n'Talk to me again and I'll have some nice stuff for you.'
'Here you go... a big 'ol bag of [placeholder] stuff. Have fun in Rohan. Bring me back a pony!'
By completing this quest, you will receive a set of Landscape Gear.
